<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px; line-height: 1.6; }
    h1 { color: #333; }
    h2 { color: #555; }
    p { max-width: 800px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>
  
  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>Welcome to our application. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our app, particularly in connection with our management of Facebook Pages. Please read this policy carefully.</p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, and other details you provide when registering or contacting us.</li>
    <li><strong>Page Messaging Data:</strong> With the <code>pages_messaging</code> permission, we collect messages sent to and from Facebook Pages you manage through our app, including message content, sender/recipient details, and timestamps.</li>
    <li><strong>Page Engagement Data:</strong> With the <code>pages_read_engagement</code> permission, we collect data related to posts, comments, likes, reactions, and other engagement metrics on Facebook Pages you manage.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our app, such as pages visited, time spent, and interactions.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and IP address.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Facilitate communication through Facebook Pages, including sending and receiving messages on your behalf.</li>
    <li>Analyze engagement metrics (e.g., likes, comments, reactions) to provide insights and improve Page performance.</li>
    <li>Provide and enhance our app’s functionality and user experience.</li>
    <li>Communicate with you, including responding to inquiries.</li>
    <li>Monitor and analyze usage patterns to optimize our services.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do not share your personal or Page-related information with third parties except:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>With service providers who assist in operating our app (e.g., hosting services or analytics tools), under strict confidentiality agreements.</li>
    <li>When required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
    <li>With Meta, as necessary to facilitate Page messaging and engagement functionalities via their APIs.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
    <li>Request deletion of messages or engagement data associated with Pages you manage, subject to Meta’s data retention policies.</li>
    <li>Revoke our app’s access to your Facebook Pages via your Facebook account settings.</li>
    <li>Contact us with privacy concerns at <%= contactEmail %>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data, including encryption for message data in transit. However, no method is 100% secure. Please use our app responsibly.</p>

  <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain Page messaging and engagement data only as long as necessary to provide our services or as required by law. You can request deletion of specific data, subject to Meta’s platform policies.</p>

  <h2>8. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Our app integrates with Meta’s APIs to manage Page messaging and engagement. Data processed through these APIs is subject to <a href="https://www.facebook.com/privacy/policy">Meta’s Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page, and we will notify you via email or in-app notifications.</p>

  <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>For questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
  <p>Email: <%= contactEmail %><br>Address: <%= companyAddress %></p>
</body>
</html>